== Usage ==
This template can be used to mark articles or sections with old or out-of-date information. Add details on what needs update on the talkpage.

This template will add articles to [[:Category:Articles in need of updating]].

==Alternatives==
*If there is a dispute about the need for an update, an out-of-date article or section can be marked with [[Template:Out of date]].
*[[Template:Update after]] is an alternative for individual statements that will be out-of-date at a specifiable future date. It is a more recent and preferred alternative to [[Wikipedia:As of]].  It also adds articles to [[:Category:Articles in need of updating]].


